  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The recovered turtle returned to the sea",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 100-kilogram turtle, which was caught in a fishing net in the Mirissa sea and suffered serious injuries in the neck area after being treated by the Hikkaduwa wildlife officials, was released back into the sea this morning (15th) at the Ambalangoda beach.",
        "This turtle was receiving treatment for several days at a turtle conservation center in Ambalangoda.",
        "Wildlife authorities decided that this turtle, which recovered quickly from the treatment of wildlife doctors and Hikkaduwa Wildlife Office officials, should be released back into the sea.",
        "Accordingly, this large turtle was released into the sea today (15) morning at Ambalangoda beach screen under the supervision of Hikkaduwa wildlife officers."
      ],
